- contribution = @notification.contribution
br
|Muraho, #{contribution.user.name}!
br
br
|Murakoze #{contribution.project.total_contributions - 1} n'abandi baterankunga, #{link_to(contribution.project.name, "#{Configuration[:base_url]}/projects/#{contribution.project.to_param}")} yasshyikirijwe neza #{Configuration[:company_name]}. Hamwe, Mwazamuye #{contribution.project.display_pledged}, Igiteranyo #{contribution.project.progress}% cy'itengo!
br/
br/
|Komeza - Nta kindi mukenye gukora kuru ubu. #{contribution.project.user.display_name} turabamenyesha vuba aha. Niba mwahisemo guhabwa ishimwe risaba amakuru ahagije, nyiri umushinga araza kubamenyesha vuba.
br
br
|Hagati aho, sangiza, ibi ku bandi bose!
br
br
- fb_img = "<img src=\"#{Configuration[:base_url]}/assets/mails/facebook-icon.png\" title='Facebook' class='social' />".html_safe
= raw link_to(fb_img, "http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=#{project_url(contribution.project)}" , target: :blank)
- twitter_img = "<img src='#{Configuration[:base_url]}/assets/mails/twitter-icon.png' title='Twitter' class='social' />".html_safe
= raw link_to(twitter_img,"http://twitter.com/?status=#{"Success! I helped greenlight #{contribution.project.name} on @#{Configuration[:twitter_username]}! #{project_url(contribution.project)}"}", target: :blank)
br
br
br
|Amakuru y'ingenzi arebana n'inkunga yawe:
br
br
|Uko inkunga ingana: 
strong #{number_to_currency contribution.value, precision: 0}
br
br
- if contribution.reward
  |Reward Selected: 
  strong #{number_to_currency contribution.reward.minimum_value, precision: 0}
  |  &mdash; #{contribution.reward.description}
  br
  br
|Itariki inkunga yatangiwe: 
strong #{l contribution.created_at.to_date, format: :long}
br
br
|Urufunguzo rw'inkunga: 
strong #{contribution.key}
br
br
|Niba mwifuza kwandikira #{contribution.project.user.name}, mwakohereza email  #{mail_to contribution.project.user.email}
br
br
|Mwaba mufize ibindi bibazo mwibaza, Mwasura paji irimo ibibazo bikunze kwibazwa #{link_to('FAQ', "#{Configuration[:base_url]}/faq")}.
br
br
|Murakoze,
br
|Ubuyobozi bwa #{Configuration[:company_name]} 
